<paragraph blockId="14.[140,1108,1504,1654]" pageId="14" pageNumber="61">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[140,302,1504,1526]" pageId="14" pageNumber="61">Figures 20–23.</emphasis>
Male terminalia for Panamanian 
